cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing tasks such as translation and proposes a modification to self-attention networks to improve their performance. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a learnable Gaussian bias to improve the performance of self-attention networks. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is a possibility as self-attention networks have been used in computer vision tasks as well, but the focus of this paper is on natural language processing. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possibility as the paper proposes a modification to a popular AI technique (self-attention networks) to improve its performance. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possibility as the paper deals with neural networks and proposes a modification to improve their performance.
